OL,3,CBBC presenter Jay Blades charged with
OL,4,C'controlling and coercive behaviour'
OL,6,FIt's currently unclear if future
OL,7,Fepisodes of the Repair Shop will be
OL,8,Fscreened, ITV News' Correspondent Neil
OL,9,FConnery reports
OL,11,FBBC presenter Jay Blades has been
OL,12,Fcharged with engaging in controlling
OL,13,Fand coercive behaviour, West Mercia
OL,14,FPolice said.
OL,16,FHe has been charged with controlling
OL,17,Fand coercive behaviour against his
OL,18,Festranged wife Lisa Zbozen, including
OL,19,Fphysical and emotional abuse, court
OL,20,Fdocuments show.
