OL,3,CBBC presenter Jay Blades charged with
OL,4,C'controlling and coercive behaviour'
OL,6,FThe 54-year-old, appeared at
OL,7,FKidderminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,FFriday after being charged by West
OL,9,FMercia Police with one count of
OL,10,Fengaging in controlling or coercive
OL,11,Fbehaviour in an intimate or family
OL,12,Frelationship.
OL,14,FThe charge relates to his fitness
OL,15,Finstructor wife Lisa Zbozen, who
OL,16,Fannounced on her Instagram page in May
OL,17,Fthat their relationship was over,
OL,18,Faccording to court documents.
