OL,3,CBBC presenter Jay Blades charged with
OL,4,C'controlling and coercive behaviour'
OL,6,FThe couple married in the grounds of a
OL,7,Fbeachfront villa in Barbados on
OL,8,FNovember 22 2022.
OL,10,FThe presenter, who fronts primetime
OL,11,Fshow The Repair Shop, will appear at
OL,12,FWorcester Crown Court for a plea and
OL,13,Ftrial preparation hearing on October
OL,14,F11.
OL,16,FIn a statement, West Mercia Police
OL,17,Fsaid: "54-year-old Jason Blades of
OL,18,FClaverley in Wolverhampton has been
OL,19,Fcharged with controlling and coercive
OL,20,Fbehaviour.
