OL,3,CBBC presenter Jay Blades charged with
OL,4,C'controlling and coercive behaviour'
OL,6,F"He appeared at Kidderminster
OL,7,FMagistrates Court this morning (Friday
OL,8,F13th September) and has been bailed to
OL,9,Fappear at Worcester Crown Court on
OL,10,FFriday 11th October."
OL,12,FFurniture restorer Blades, who grew up
OL,13,Fin Hackney, was made an MBE for
OL,14,Fservices to craft in 2022.
OL,16,FHe found fame on The Repair Shop, the
OL,17,Frestoration programme he has presented
OL,18,Fsince 2017, which sees members of the
OL,19,Fpublic take worn-out family heirlooms
OL,20,Fto be restored by a team of experts.
